{
  "title": "External Secrets Operator - Overview",
  "description": "The External Secrets Operator (ESO) synchronizes secrets from external providers (e.g. HashiCorp Vault) into Kubernetes Secrets. This dashboard provides visibility into ESO's health and performance, including reconciliation rates, provider API calls, secret sync status, and controller runtime metrics.\n\n**Further reading:**\n\n- [External Secrets Operator Docs](https://external-secrets.io/)\n- [Metrics Reference](https://external-secrets.io/latest/api/metrics/)",
